### 変数定義
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api/v1
@token = 

### ===== 認証 =====

### ログイン
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "sales@gmail.com",
  "password": "password"
}

### ログイン後、上記のレスポンスからtokenをコピーして @token に貼り付けてください


### ===== 認証確認 =====

### ログイン中のユーザー情報取得
GET {{baseUrl}}/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ===== 顧客管理 =====

### 顧客一覧取得
GET {{baseUrl}}/customers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 顧客詳細取得
GET {{baseUrl}}/customers/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 顧客新規作成
POST {{baseUrl}}/customers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "company_name": "新規テスト株式会社",
  "industry": "IT",
  "phone": "03-9999-9999",
  "address": "東京都新宿区"
}

### 顧客更新
PUT {{baseUrl}}/customers/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "company_name": "株式会社サンプル商事（更新）",
  "industry": "製造業",
  "phone": "03-1234-5678",
  "address": "東京都千代田区丸の内1-1-1"
}

### 顧客削除
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/customers/999
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ===== 担当者管理 =====

### 担当者一覧取得
GET {{baseUrl}}/contacts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 担当者新規作成
POST {{baseUrl}}/contacts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer_id": 1,
  "name": "テスト太郎",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "phone": "090-1234-5678",
  "position": "担当者"
}


### ===== 商談管理 =====

### 商談一覧取得
GET {{baseUrl}}/deals
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 商談新規作成
POST {{baseUrl}}/deals
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer_id": 1,
  "title": "新規システム導入案件",
  "amount": 5000000,
  "status": "見込み",
  "close_date": "2026-03-31"
}


### ===== 活動履歴 =====

### 活動履歴一覧取得
GET {{baseUrl}}/activities
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 活動履歴新規作成
POST {{baseUrl}}/activities
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer_id": 1,
  "type": "訪問",
  "description": "新規システムの提案を実施",
  "activity_date": "2026-02-23"
}


### ===== タスク管理 =====

### タスク一覧取得
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### タスク新規作成
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "見積書作成",
  "description": "新規システム導入の見積書を作成する",
  "status": "未着手",
  "due_date": "2026-02-28"
}


### ===== ログアウト =====

### ログアウト
POST {{baseUrl}}/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
